text: Of cleuan hithe on yone mide mestan thorn bi thyythe to landscharleighe on Wormester ist andlang ifre on Wormesleighe welle þanen on ya vor saide ake on humberwe stede.
Of gere ak on þa tyo sirsas þanen on thar eorðbriste and þanen on ruwanleighe on þan ealde heierewe þanen on þan schiren mor midward.
And soa west after streme bitwixe bradan mede and driganhurste soa forth bi suthene herthine on tettanstaples þanen on clewan hithe on þan midde mestan thorn.
